---
title: Grilled Tuscan Chicken Thighs Penne with Sun-Dried Tomato Sauce
description: Elevate your pasta night with this grilled chicken penne! Juicy grilled chicken, zucchini, and tomatoes combine with al dente pasta for a taste of Tuscany in every bite. A rustic medley of flavors, kissed by the grill and tossed together for a satisfying meal that transports you to the heart of Italy with each forkful!
